1865
02:05:28,200 --> 02:05:30,368
<i>Had Grace had friends in Dogville,</i>

1866
02:05:30,733 --> 02:05:33,600
<i>they too fell like the leaves.</i>

1867
02:05:35,367 --> 02:05:37,445
<i>Most townspeople of the male sex</i>

1868
02:05:37,800 --> 02:05:39,798
<i>now visited Grace at night</i>

1869
02:05:39,934 --> 02:05:42,012
<i>to fulfill their sexual needs.</i>

1870
02:05:43,867 --> 02:05:46,325
<i>It had occurred to the children
to give the bell an extra ring</i>

1871
02:05:46,733 --> 02:05:49,720
<i>every time such an act
