<i>much to Martha's confusion.</i>

1873
02:05:54,301 --> 02:05:56,469
<i>But since the chain
had been attached,</i>

1874
02:05:56,833 --> 02:05:59,461
<i>things had become easier
for everyone.</i>

1875
02:06:00,867 --> 02:06:04,374
<i>The harassments in bed did not have
